@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>
    Welcome to **Ahmed's Hospital Management System**. This system is designed to enhance hospital efficiency while ensuring the security and confidentiality of patient data.
    We are committed to protecting personal information and providing secure healthcare management.
</p>

<h2>🔒 Data Protection & Security</h2>
<p>
    - All patient records are securely stored and **never shared with third parties** without explicit consent.
    - We use **advanced encryption** and strict authentication mechanisms to ensure data safety.
    - User access is controlled via **ASP.NET Core Identity**, allowing only authorized personnel to view and manage sensitive information.
</p>

<h2>📜 Information Usage</h2>
<p>
    - Patient and hospital data is used **solely for healthcare management purposes**.
    - The system collects and stores only necessary information to improve medical care and streamline hospital operations.
    - Users have the right to request **modifications or deletions** of their stored data upon approval.
</p>

<h2>✅ Compliance & Updates</h2>
<p>
    - The system follows **standard healthcare regulations** to ensure compliance with data protection laws.
    - Regular security updates and audits are performed to maintain system integrity.
    - Any changes to this privacy policy will be communicated transparently to users.
</p>

<p>
    Thank you for trusting **Ahmed's Hospital Management System**. Your privacy and data security are our top priorities.
</p>